definition:
A man living at the time of United Monarchy, first mentioned at 2Sa.17.25; married to Abigail (H0026H); 
 father of: Amasa (H6021); also called Ithra at 2Sa.17.25;
Another name of ye.ter (יֶ֫תֶר "Jether" H3500H) 
 § Ithra = "abundance"
 father of Amasa, the commander of Absalom's army; also 'Jether'
